3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a new protocol for relay networks, which can be seen as a control system. The paper also discusses the scheduling scheme for the proposed protocol, which is a topic of interest in control systems.
4. cs.COMM (Computer Communications and Networks) - The paper deals with a relay channel and proposes a new protocol to improve its performance, which is a topic of interest in computer communications and networks.
